# Testing

- Vitest + React Testing Library for unit + integration.
- Playwright for E2E; one happy path per critical journey.
- MSW for network in tests.
- Behavior assertions, not implementation.
- Query by role / label / text. `getByTestId` only when no semantic query exists.
- Every bug fix ships a regression test.
- Coverage gates: 80% lines / 75% branches / 80% functions.
- No snapshot tests as a substitute for assertions.
See `.opencode/agents/testing.md`.